sections.text:
2004 Repeal.

Chapter 72 (§§ 7201 - 7205) was added December 16, 1992, P.L.1250, No.166, and repealed November 29, 2004, P.L.1376, No.178, effective immediately. The subject matter is now contained in the act of November 29, 2004 (P.L.1376, No.178), known as the Alternative Fuels Incentive Act.
